TopicTitle: I need help with airplane plus and some parts not appearing

Articles.Content: Im using 1.3.1 and i have reinstalled and tried that over and over again but some parts are just not appearing. If anyone can tell me how to fix this that will be greatly appreciated

Moved post to the Technical Support (PC, Modded) section of the forum.

Welcome aboard Captain!

I'm afraid I don't know how to fix your issue, but hopefully someone will be along shortly to help you out. In the meantime, it might be good to provide a bit more information. Are you playing in career mode? How many other mods are you using?
You can post on my thread for help. Make sure you installed it correctly. GameData must be in the root folder. This means that the GameData folder is in the same place as to where the KSP.exe is.
